posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Centerline', 'Our touring schedules and operating hours may vary as we continue to follow local phased opening guidelines and direction from local health officials.', 'Please visit our community website for up to date information.', 'Experience Seattle living at Centerline.', 'With substantial first floor retail, a private/public interior courtyard, roof-top decks with dog areas, BBQ and green roofs bring a real community feeling to the building.', "At Centerline you're right at home.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 214', 'OR Text', '214', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 688 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Wood-Style Flooring', '- Generous Closets', '- Brand New Apartments', '- Floor-to-Ceiling Windows', '- Modern Kitchens', 'Community Amenities', '- Green Roofs', '- Ground Floor Retail', '- Interior Courtyard', '- Parking Garage', '- Rooftop Decks & BBQ Areas', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Centerline', '1420 NE 65th', 'St, Seattle, WA, 98115', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '0a7Snwzf']
